1. Download terraform 
$ mkdir terraform; cd terraform
----------------------
2. Download terraform
govinda@govinda:~/backup2/terraform$ wget https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/0.11.2/terraform_0.11.2_linux_amd64.zip

3. Unzip terraform
govinda@govinda:~/backup2/terraform$ unzip terraform_0.11.2_linux_amd64.zip
4. move terraform to /usr/local/bin/
$  mv terraform /usr/local/bin/

5. Step 4 we can do another way by specifying path on ~/.profile
$ vim ~/.profile
## Add this line at the button of files

export PATH=$path:/location of file
save and exit from terminal

reopen the terminal

6. Chack terraform is installed correctly or not you get this kind of result
$ terraform -version
Terraform v0.11.2

7. your terraform is installed correclty 


 

 
 





